 Hipgnosis 竞购战升级，黑石达成 16 亿美元交易https://www.nme.com/news/music/bidding-war-for-hipgnosis-escalates-with-blackstone-striking-1-6billion-deal-3751697?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bidding-war-for- hipgnosis 与黑石集团达成 1-60 亿美元交易升级Liberty DunworthMon, 29 Apr 2024 10:15:04 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativePopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3751697 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>通过此次交易，Blackstone 的音乐版权组合中将添加超过 65,000 首歌曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bidding-war-for-hipgnosis-escalates-with-blackstone-striking-1-6billion-deal-3751697">随着 Blackstone 达成 16 亿美元的交易，Hipgnosis 的竞购战进一步升级，该交易</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis-Nile-Rodgers-Merck-Mercuriadis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Hipgnosis Song Fund 的竞购战已经升级，黑石集团已同意以 16 亿美元（12.8 亿英镑）收购该公司。</p><p>通过这笔交易，Blackstone 对音乐版权投资者的估值为每股 1.30 美元（1.04 英镑），并且超过了 Concord 之前对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shakira">夏奇拉</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">艾德·希兰</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">红辣椒</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/neil-young">尼尔·杨</a>等艺术家的音乐权的报价。 Concord 提出的报价为每股 1.25 美元（1 英镑）。</p><p> Blackstone 已获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-bieber">贾斯汀·比伯 (Justin Bieber)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-timberlake">贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake)</a>歌曲的版权，目前的交易将使超过 65,000 首歌曲添加到其目录中。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/blackstone-outbids-concord-16-bln-takeover-battle-hipgnosis-2024-04-29/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>路透社</em></a>强调，黑石集团还投资了美国表演权组织 SESAC，该组织的附属机构包括摇滚老将<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-dylan">鲍勃·迪伦</a>和 16 届格莱美奖得主<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">阿黛尔</a>。</p><p>今天（4 月 29 日），该公司提出了 16 亿美元的报价，就在几天前，Concord 的出价比该公司高出 10 美分，并赢得了 Hipgnosis 董事会对这笔交易的支持。此后，Hipgnosis 撤回了对该要约的建议，并跟进了 Blackstone 的要约。</p><p> Hipgnosis 董事长罗伯特·内勒 (Robert Naylor) 在一份新声明中（<em>路透社</em>）表示：“我们很高兴，在收购 Hipgnosis 的竞争中，我们的投资者现在有机会立即以更高的溢价变现其持有的股份。”</p><p> Blackstone 是 Hipgnosis 投资顾问 HSM 的大股东。该顾问负责管理该基金的艺术家和词曲作者，并持有看涨期权，如果他们的咨询协议终止，可以对 Hipgnosis 的投资组合提出更高的报价。 </p><figure id="attachment_3751700" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3751700" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3751700" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Hipgnosis 歌曲基金徽标出现在智能手机和电脑屏幕上。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hipgnosis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3751700" class="wp-caption-text"> Hipgnosis 歌曲基金徽标出现在智能手机和电脑屏幕上。 （照片插图：Pavlo Gonchar/SOPA Images/LightRocket via Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>这笔交易的消息传出之前，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chic">别致传奇</a>人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nile-rodgers">尼罗·罗杰斯 (Nile Rodgers)</a>和默克·默库里亚迪斯 (Merck Mercuriadis)（艾尔顿·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">约翰 (Elton John)</a>和碧昂丝<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">(Beyoncé</a> ) 的前经纪人）创立并发起的音乐基金去年陷入财务困境。其中包括对估值、董事会和法律纠纷的担忧，以及股东对目录销售交易的反抗。</p><p>去年 12 月，Hipgnosis 原本打算分享其半年业绩，但表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/hipgnosis-song-fund-delays-financial-results-over-concerns-songs-are-being-under-valued-3561263">由于担心音乐目录和歌曲的估值不够高而推迟公布业绩</a>。</p><p>据报道，3 月份， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hipgnosis-stock-hits-record-low-as-value-of-music-portfolio-plummets-3596878">歌曲基金创下了历史新低，因为一项审查估计其目录的公允价值在 18 亿英镑至略高于 20 亿英镑之间</a>。该报告由其首席顾问 Shot Tower 完成，显示其价值比 Hipgnosis 2023 年 9 月报告的价值至少下降了五分之一。</p><p>有报道称，该品牌<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hipgnosis-has-spent-1billion-on-artist-catalogues-in-the-past-year-2986301">在 2021 年斥资 10 亿美元（7.2 亿英镑）收购艺术家过往作品，</a>此后股价创下历史新低。其中包括购买<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lindsey-buckingham">Lindsey Buckingham</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blondies-debbie-harry-and-chris-stein-sell-rights-to-future-royalties-2722458">Blondie</a>等艺术家的目录，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jimmy-iovine-sells-worldwide-producer-royalties-to-hipgnosis-song-fund-2848901">Jimmy Iovine 的全球制作人版税</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-young-sells-half-of-his-song-catalogue-for-around-150-million-2850112">Neil Young 一半的歌曲，</a>这笔交易估计价值 1.5 亿美元（1.1 亿英镑）。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shakira">夏奇拉</a>还将她所有 145 首歌曲卖给了 Hipgnosis，包括《Hips Don&#39;t Lie》、《She Wolf》和《Whenever,Wherever》，这些都是交易的一部分。</p><p>当时，麦库里亚迪斯表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hipgnosis-boss-says-cultural-relevance-of-artists-is-key-to-back-catalogues-they-have-acquired-2855597">，对于那些已获得过往作品目录的艺术家来说，文化重要性是关键。</a></p><p> “因此，我们投入了超过 10 亿英镑，但只拥有 57,000 首歌曲。但其中有 10,000 首是前 10 首歌曲，其中近 3,000 首是第一名歌曲。因此，相对于环球、华纳或索尼来说，这是一个非常小的目录。但该目录中成功的比例非常高，很少有歌曲不成功。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bidding-war-for-hipgnosis-escalates-with-blackstone-striking-1-6billion-deal-3751697">随着 Blackstone 达成 16 亿美元的交易，Hipgnosis 的竞购战进一步升级，该交易</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 U2 成员亚当·克莱顿 (Adam Clayton) 与妻子玛丽安娜 (Mariana) 宣布离婚https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2s-adam-clayton-and-wife-mariana-announce-divorce-3751678?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=u2s-adam-clayton-and-wife-mariana-宣布离婚Hollie GeraghtyMon, 29 Apr 2024 10:02:45 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3751678 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/adam-clayton-divorce.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Mariana Teixeira De Carvalho（左）和音乐家 Adam Clayton" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/adam-clayton-divorce.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/adam-clayton-divorce-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/adam-clayton-divorce-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/adam-clayton-divorce-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/adam-clayton-divorce-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/adam-clayton-divorce-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一位发言人表示，这对夫妇在一起十多年后“友好离婚”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2s-adam-clayton-and-wife-mariana-announce-divorce-3751678">U2 乐队成员 Adam Clayton 和妻子 Mariana 宣布离婚的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/adam-clayton-divorce.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Mariana Teixeira De Carvalho（左）和音乐家 Adam Clayton" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/adam-clayton-divorce.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/adam-clayton-divorce-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/adam-clayton-divorce-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/adam-clayton-divorce-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024