c" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Post-Malone-Taylor-Swift-Florence-Welch@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Post-Malone-Taylor-Swift-Florence-Welch@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Post-Malone-Taylor-Swift-Florence-Welch@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Post-Malone-Taylor-Swift-Florence-Welch@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Post-Malone-Taylor-Swift-Florence-Welch@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Post-Malone-Taylor-Swift-Florence-Welch@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>与合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/post-malone">波斯特·马龙</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-welch">弗洛伦斯·韦尔奇</a>分享了一系列她的照片，庆祝<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">“折磨诗人部门”</a>的持续成功。看看下面的内容。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）——《受折磨的诗人部》评论：罕见的失误</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（4 月 28 日），这位流行偶像在 Instagram 上分享了这些宝丽来照片，庆祝她的新专辑首次登上 Billboard 200 排行榜第一名，并在美国销量超过 260 万张。</p><p> “我的心被震撼了。我完全被你对这张专辑所表现出的爱所震惊，”她在标题中开始说道。 “260万你是认真的吗？？感谢您收听、直播并欢迎折磨诗人进入您的生活。感觉完全不知所措。”</p><p> “我已经迫不及待地想要回到巡演了，但你却这么做了？ 5 月 9 日来得太快了，”她补充道，指的是她即将到来的<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-kick-off-top-five-moments-from-the-stars-transcendent-performance-3416005">“Eras Tour”</a>日期，该日期将于下个月在巴黎恢复。</p><p>帖子中展示了这位“午夜”歌手在“折磨诗人部门”录音期间的各种照片，以及她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/post-malone-and-florence-the-machine-to-feature-on-taylor-swifts-the-tortured-poets-department-3583153">客座合作者波斯特·马龙和弗洛伦斯·韦尔奇</a>的两张照片。这位说唱歌手出演了开场曲目<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-drops-video-for-post-malone-collaboration-fortnight-3689827">“Fortnight”</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-and-the-machine">Florence + The Machine 的</a>主唱则与斯威夫特一起演唱了一首名为“Florida!!!”的歌曲。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6USF85OdFC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C52