rics-tracklist-3619454">对《折磨诗人部》的三星级评论</a>中表示：“斯威夫特似乎在孜孜不倦地追求超级巨星，但随之而来的负面公众舆论却让她感到厌烦，这是一个令人厌倦的主题，现在困扰着她的唱片和几乎没有留下她擅长的辛酸抒情观察的空间。</p><p> “这就是为什么她的第 11 张录音室专辑陷入的陷阱更加令人失望——她一次又一次地证明了她可以做得更好。斯威夫特对参加“Eras Tour”的墨尔本观众说，“受折磨的诗人部”来自于写作的“需要”。只是也许我们不需要听到它。” </p><figure id="attachment_3619469" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3619469" style="width: 3000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3619469" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department.jpg" alt="泰勒斯威夫特" width="3000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department.jpg 3000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3619469" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒·斯威夫特《The Tortured Poets Department》专辑封面</figcaption></figure><p>专辑发行后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-think-taylor-swift-wrote-the-tortured-poets-department-about-matty-healy-3619865">人们猜测这张专辑的大部分内容都是关于 1975 年的主唱马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy)</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-music-undergoes-streaming-rise-amid-reports-of-taylor-swift-romance-3443019">去年他和斯威夫特有过一段短暂的关系</a>。传闻与他有关的歌曲包括主打歌《有史以来最小的人》等。最近几天， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-matty-healy-respond-to-taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-3750415">希利</a>和他的母亲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-frontman-matty-healy-mum-denise-welch-responds-taylor-swift-tortured-poets-department-3751117">丹尼斯·韦尔奇都分享了他们对这张专辑的回应</a>。</p><p>如前所述，这位流行歌星将于下个月在巴黎开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-international-dates-for-eras-tour-3458456">她职业生涯的大型巡演的欧洲和英国/爱尔兰站</a>，并将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramores-hayley-williams-says-shes-so-ready-to-tour-with-taylor-swift-praises-the-tortured-poets-department-3749597">帕拉莫尔</a>一起在伦敦举办<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-adds-two-new-london-eras-shows-with-paramore-3538573">八场演唱会，门票全部售完</a>。有人猜测，由于她与波斯特·马龙合作的单曲《双周》配乐的排练片段， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-shares-eras-tour-rehearsals-video-could-tortured-poets-be-added-to-the-setlist-3750980">《折磨的诗人》可能会出现在歌单中</a>。</p><p>同样，在最近的一次采访中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-welch">弗洛伦斯·韦尔奇</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/florence-welch-talks-taylor-swift-collaboration-hints-at-eras-tour-appearance-in-london-3750496">暗示她可能会惊喜地出现在首都的舞台上</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-shares-polaroids-post-malone-florence-welch-tortured-poets-department-3751656">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 与波斯特·马龙 (Post Malone) 和弗洛伦斯·韦尔奇 (Florence Welch) 分享工作室拍立得照片，《折磨诗人部门》在美国的销量超过 260 万张，这一消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
